headline: Walmart, bonds, and how the labor market is 'hanging in there'
summary: Investors are watching how tariffs and a cooling labor market could impact fixed income opportunities. MassMutual Portfolio Manager Kelly Kowalski joins Catalysts to discuss why Walmart (WMT) stands out for its credit quality and ability to withstand economic pressure. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Catalysts here.
